# Override .gitignore deny-all for ripgrep/search tools.
# The .gitignore uses `*` (deny-all) + allowlist, which causes rg
# to skip force-added files. This file restores search visibility.
!*
var/tmp/
var/eca/
var/autosave/
var/backup/
var/cache/
var/lockfiles/
var/undo-fu-session/
var/tramp-autosave/
var/tree-sitter/
